Amadou Aboubakar Zaki (amụrụ ya na 10 Febụwarị 1988) bụ onye Nigiria na-agba bọọlụ, onye na-agba na Union Rennes Basket iri atọ na ise
Na-eguzo na 7 ft 0 in (2.13 m), Zaki na-egwuri egwu dị ka onye na-aga n'ihu ma ọ bụ onye etiti
Zaki agbaala bọọlụ na France na Denmark dị ka onye ọkpụkpọ ọkachamara.
